      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition \u2014 buyers should come in with realistic expectations. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple areas of paint fading, scratches, and surface rust in several locations. The body panels have visible dents and dings that have accumulated over the years, and the trim pieces show considerable deterioration. The interior is similarly worn: the upholstery is torn and stained in multiple spots, the dashboard has cracks, and some of the controls and features may not function reliably. Mechanically, the car runs but requires attention \u2014 expect that repairs and maintenance will be needed in the near term. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in bringing it up to a better standard. We are pricing this vehicle accordingly and transparently to reflect its true current state.",
